channel.description:
Hey guys!
Just released a new song, but this time, I decided to mix it up, and by that, I mean mix two genres. It’s not the best track ever, but if you would be willing to listen a provide feedback, that would be much appreciated.
P.s. Huge thanks to @Lex for helping me get started!
Enjoy:
